I have a temperature in Farenheit

Insert Farenheit temp into form field C = 5/9 (F-32

	When I click convert to Celcius {
		Subtract 32 from Farenheit temp
		Multipy new value by 5/9
		Display the new temperature on the page/in celcius form field
	}

I have a temperature in Celcius.

Insert Celcius temp into form field 

	When I click convert to Farenheit {
		Add 32 to Celcius temp
		Multipy new value by 1.8
		Display the new temperature on the page/in farenheit form field form field
	}


	relevant formulas:
	C = 5/9 (F-32)
	F = 9/5 (C+32)